Author: wrappedinlust
Text: i don't understand why do they feel entitled to have opinions on my disorder? i mean, is an illness. You are not a certified professional who i trust, shut up.  I get that for the people that care for me can be scary. But the ones who comment are usually people i have no real relationship with.

Author: blackplumsummer
Text: Preach!! Other people (my coworkers mostly) involving themselves in my ED and trying to force me to eat drives me crazy. It's none of their business if I skip lunch or not, it has no impact my work ethic.
